Furthermore, the shrine building dismantled after the merger was relocated to Kasuga Shrine in Seikechō, {{ill|Oita City|ja|大分市}} – the building having been lost in the {{ill|Oita Air Raid|ja|大分空襲}} in July {{ill|1945|ja|1945}} (Shōwa 20) – and was used as its main hall. After a new main hall was constructed for Kasuga Shrine in {{ill|1967|ja|1967}}, the former building has served as a storehouse for the mikoshi.<ref name="oita-press_2018-07-20" />
